- It's OK, John. He's not resisting...

871
00:53:43,090 --> 00:53:45,000
不  這怎麼會沒關係  這太荒謬了
No, it's not all right, this is ridiculous.

872
00:53:45,080 --> 00:53:46,800
現在帶他下樓
Get him downstairs now.

873
00:53:47,770 --> 00:53:48,690
