You really don't have to do this.

874
00:53:48,690 --> 00:53:51,160
別妨礙公務  不然我連你一起逮捕
Don't try to interfere or I shall arrest you too.

875
00:53:55,350 --> 00:53:56,270
你滿意了嗎
You done?

876
00:53:56,270 --> 00:53:57,500
我早就說過
I said it.

877
00:53:57,970 --> 00:53:59,370
- 我們初次見面的時候  - 算了吧
- First time we met. - Don't bother.

878
00:53:59,370 --> 00:54:01,020
