Solving crimes won't be enough.

879
00:54:01,920 --> 00:54:03,660
總有一天  他會越過底線
One day he'll cross the line.

880
00:54:04,260 --> 00:54:07,470
你自己想想  什麼人會去綁架孩子
Now ask yourself, what sort of man would kidnap those kids

881
00:54:07,470 --> 00:54:09,870
就為了通過找回他們來顯擺自己
just so he can impress us all by finding them?

882
00:54:10,010 --> 00:54:11,300
- 多諾萬  - 長官
- Donovan? - Sir?

883
00:54:11,300 --> 00:54:14,260
- 人抓住了嗎  - 是的  長官
- Got our man? - Yes, sir.

884
00:54:14,420 --> 00:54:16,890
要我說的話  看著他就覺得古怪
Looked a bit of a weirdo, if you ask me.

885
00:54:16,900 --> 00:54:20,130
這種義警通常都這樣
Often are, these vigilante types.

886
00:54:22,260 --> 00:54:23,590
你看什麼呢
What are you looking at?

887
00:54:25,930 --> 00:54:27,180
你還好嗎  長官
Are you all right, sir?

888
00:54:29,240 --> 00:54:31,390
- 來跟我作伴了  - 是的
