麥考夫  他能幫我們
Mycroft, he could help us.

918
00:56:01,320 --> 00:56:04,170
現在真不是打親情牌的好時機
Big family reconciliation, now's not really the moment.

919
00:56:06,690 --> 00:56:07,960
夏洛克
Sherlock...

920
00:56:08,100 --> 00:56:08,970
有人跟來了
we're being followed.

921
00:56:08,970 --> 00:56:10,300
我就知道躲不過警察
I knew we couldn't outrun the police.

922
