那人不是警察
That's not the police,

923
00:56:11,160 --> 00:56:12,950
是咱們貝克街上的新鄰居
it's one of my new neighbours from Baker Street.

924
00:56:13,690 --> 00:56:15,190
看他能不能給我們答案
Let's see if he can give us some answers.

925
00:56:21,190 --> 00:56:22,590
我們去哪兒
Where are we going?

926
00:56:23,800 --> 00:56:25,290
我們要衝到那輛巴士前面
We're going to jump in front of that bus.

927
00:56:37,400 --> 00:56:38,620
你想從我這裏得到什麼
Tell me what you want from me.

928
00:56:39,910 --> 00:56:40,720
告訴我
Tell me!

929
