這就是你的爆料人
So that's your source?

974
00:59:10,640 --> 00:59:12,400
莫裏亞蒂就是理查·布魯克
Moriarty is Richard Brook?

975
00:59:12,400 --> 00:59:15,160
他就是理查·布魯克  不存在莫裏亞蒂
Of course he's Richard Brook, there is no Moriarty.

976
00:59:15,710 --> 00:59:16,830
從來就沒有這個人
There never has been.

977
00:59:16,830 --> 00:59:18,630
- 你說什麼胡話  - 仔細看看他
- What are you talking about? - Look him up.

978
00:59:19,150 --> 00:59:23,860
理查·布魯克  夏洛克雇來扮演莫裏亞蒂的人
Rich Brook, an actor Sherlock Holmes hired to be Moriarty.

979
00:59:29,240 --> 00:59:32,000
