你剛剛知道嗎
You're just getting that now? Wo- wo- wo!

1192
01:12:47,750 --> 01:12:48,870
好吧
Ok.

1193
01:12:50,840 --> 01:12:52,950
我再給你點動力
Let me give you a little extra incentive.

1194
01:12:53,790 --> 01:12:56,190
要是你不跳  你朋友就會死
Your friends will die if you don't.

1195
01:12:57,700 --> 01:13:01,180
