What did I miss?

1221
01:15:01,490 --> 01:15:03,210
你不會這麼做
You're not going to do it.

1222
01:15:03,970 --> 01:15:05,070
所以還有辦法讓殺手收手
So the killers can be called off,

1223
01:15:05,070 --> 01:15:08,720
有個代碼  暗號或數字
then there's a recall code or a word or a number.

1224
01:15:11,300 --> 01:15:12,620
如果我有你
I don't have to die

1225
01:15:14,020 --> 01:15:15,770
我就不用死
if I've got you.

1226
01:15:18,450 --> 01:15:20,290
你覺得你能讓我下令讓他們住手嗎
You think you can make me stop the order?

1227
01:15:20,300 --> 01:15:22,930
- 你覺得你能做到嗎  - 當然
- You think you can make me do that? - Yes.

1228
01:15:24,810 --> 01:15:28,110
- 你也這麼覺得  - 夏洛克  你哥哥和整個政府的人
- So do you. - Sherlock, your big brother and all the King's horses

1229
01:15:28,110 --> 01:15:30,080
都不能逼我做我不想做的事
couldn't make me do a thing I didn't want to.

1230
01:15:30,080 --> 01:15:32,410
是的  但我不是我哥哥  記得嗎
Yes, but I'm not my brother, remember?

1231
01:15:34,510 --> 01:15:35,790
我是你
I am you.

1232
01:15:36,330 --> 01:15:37,930
準備好做任何事
Prepared to do anything.

1233
01:15:38,590 --> 01:15:40,100
準備好毀滅一切
Prepared to burn.

1234
01:15:40,720 --> 01:15:43,420
準備好做普通人做不到的事
Prepared to do what ordinary people won't do.

1235
01:15:44,250 --> 01:15:46,010
