You want me to shake hands with you in hell?

1236
01:15:46,010 --> 01:15:48,280
那我奉陪
I shall not disappoint you.

1237
01:15:50,700 --> 01:15:52,140
不
Nah.

1238
01:15:52,920 --> 01:15:54,610
