You talk big.

1239
01:15:55,990 --> 01:15:57,210
才不是呢
Nah.

1240
01:15:57,340 --> 01:15:58,900
你是普通人
You're ordinary.

1241
01:15:59,260 --> 01:16:02,380
你是普通人  你站在正義那一方
You're ordinary. You're on the side of the angels.

1242
01:16:02,490 --> 01:16:04,880
我也許是站在正義那一方
I may be on the side of the angels,

1243
01:16:05,360 --> 01:16:11,010
但這絕不代表我和他們是一種人
but don't think for one second that I am one of them.

1244
01:16:19,780 --> 01:16:20,930
對
No...

1245
01:16:23,000 --> 01:16:24,160
你不是
you're not.

1246
01:16:30,630 --> 01:16:31,710
我懂了
I see.

1247
01:16:33,830 --> 01:16:35,310
你不是普通人
You're not ordinary.

1248
01:16:36,120 --> 01:16:37,200
不是
No.

1249
01:16:38,970 --> 01:16:40,250
你是我
You're me.

1250
01:16:42,780 --> 01:16:44,050
你就是我
You're me.

1251
01:16:46,440 --> 01:16:47,670
謝謝
Thank you...

1252
01:16:49,450 --> 01:16:51,090
夏洛克·福爾摩斯
Sherlock Holmes.

1253
01:17:00,190 --> 01:17:01,510
謝謝你了
Thank you.

1254
01:17:03,340 --> 01:17:04,640
上帝保佑你
Bless you.

1255
01:17:08,250 --> 01:17:09,480
只要我還活著
As long as I'm alive,

1256
01:17:09,480 --> 01:17:12,680
你就能救你的朋友  你就會有退路
you can save your friends, you've got a way out.

1257
01:17:14,940 --> 01:17:16,370
那就祝你好運了
Well, good luck with that.

1258
01:17:18,040 --> 01:17:19,050
不
No.

1259
01:17:53,020 --> 01:17:54,780
是的  先生  謝謝  再見
Yes, sir. Thank you. Bye.

1260
01:18:39,740 --> 01:18:40,790
喂
Hello?

1261
01:18:41,090 --> 01:18:42,910
- 約翰  - 夏洛克  你沒事吧
- John. - Hey, Sherlock. Are you OK?

1262
01:18:43,380 --> 01:18:45,530
轉過身  往回走  我這就來
Turn around and walk back the way you came. I'm coming in.

1263
01:18:45,530 --> 01:18:48,150
照我說的做
Just do as I ask!

1264
01:18:48,740 --> 01:18:49,780
求你了
Please.

1265
01:18:49,840 --> 01:18:50,850
在哪
Where?

1266
01:18:53,150 --> 01:18:54,250
停在那別動
Stop there.

1267
01:18:54,820 --> 01:18:57,790
- 夏洛克  - 好了  抬頭  我在屋頂上
- Sherlock? - OK, look up. I'm on the rooftop.

1268
01:18:59,450 --> 01:19:00,750
天啊
God.

1269
01:19:01,490 --> 01:19:05,670
我不能下來  所以我們只能這麼說話了
I... I can't come down, so we'll just have to do it like this.

1270
01:19:06,850 --> 01:19:07,970
怎麼了
What's going on?

1271
01:19:08,260 --> 01:19:09,440
我要道歉
An apology.

1272
01:19:12,900 --> 01:19:14,270
這一切都是真的
It's all true.

1273
01:19:14,600 --> 01:19:15,730
什麼
What?

1274
01:19:16,400 --> 01:19:22,050
他們說的關於我的一切  我創造了莫裏亞蒂
Everything they said about me. I invented Moriarty.

1275
01:19:27,720 --> 01:19:29,130
你為什麼要這麼說
Why are you saying this?

1276
01:19:32,430 --> 01:19:33,720
我是個冒牌貨
I'm a fake.

1277
01:19:34,410 --> 01:19:37,640
- 夏洛克  - 報紙上寫的都是真的
- Sherlock... - The newspapers were right all along.

1278
01:19:38,710 --> 01:19:40,650
我要你告訴雷斯垂德
I want you to tell Lestrade,

1279
01:19:41,100 --> 01:19:44,120
告訴赫德森太太和茉莉
I want you to tell Mrs Hudson and Molly.

1280
01:19:45,290 --> 01:19:47,890
告訴所有相信你的人
In fact, tell anyone who will listen to you...

1281
01:19:49,670 --> 01:19:53,860
我為了自己創造了莫裏亞蒂
that I created Moriarty for my own purposes.

1282
01:19:54,600 --> 01:19:56,130
好了  閉嘴  夏洛克  別說了
OK, shut up Sherlock. Shut up.

1283
01:19:56,130 --> 01:19:59,070
我們第一次見面的時候
The first time we met... the first time we met,

1284
01:19:59,070 --> 01:20:02,730
- 你就對我姐姐的事瞭如指掌吧  - 沒人能這麼聰明
- you knew all about my sister, right? - Nobody could be that clever.

1285
01:20:02,900 --> 01:20:04,040
你就可以
You could.

1286
01:20:12,930 --> 01:20:14,420
我調查了你
I researched you.

1287
01:20:15,360 --> 01:20:18,360
我們見面之前  我查了所有關於你的資料
Before we met, I discovered everything that I could

1288
01:20:18,370 --> 01:20:19,740
就為了讓你印象深刻
to impress you.

1289
01:20:22,290 --> 01:20:24,630
這只是個把戲罷了
It's a trick. Just a magic trick.

1290
01:20:24,630 --> 01:20:27,010
不  快別說了
No. All right, stop it now.

1291
01:20:27,750 --> 01:20:29,750
不  站在那別動
No. Stay exactly where you are.

1292
01:20:30,660 --> 01:20:32,340
- 別動  - 好吧
- Don't move. - All right.

1293
01:20:34,610 --> 01:20:36,430
好好看著我
Keep your eyes fixed on me.

1294
01:20:37,330 --> 01:20:39,780
- 求你了  你能為我做這件事嗎  - 什麼事
- Please, will you do this for me? - Do what?

1295
01:20:40,740 --> 01:20:42,410
這通電話
This phone call, it's...

1296
01:20:43,840 --> 01:20:45,100
是我的遺言
it's my note.

1297
01:20:47,650 --> 01:20:49,340
人們都會這麼做的吧
It's what people do, don't they?

1298
01:20:51,950 --> 01:20:53,120
留遺言
Leave a note?

1299
01:20:55,550 --> 01:20:56,830
留什麼鬼遺言啊
Leave a note when?

1300
01:20:57,860 --> 01:21:00,800
- 再見  約翰  - 不  不要
- Goodbye, John. - No. Don't...

1301
01:21:11,880 --> 01:21:13,350
夏洛克
Sherlock!

1302
01:21:16,690 --> 01:21:17,790
夏洛克
Sherlock.

1303
01:22:04,430 --> 01:22:06,890
夏洛克
Sherlock... Sherlock.

1304
01:22:08,860 --> 01:22:11,980
我是醫生  讓我過去  快讓我過去
I'm a doctor, let me come through. Let me come through, please.

1305
01:22:11,990 --> 01:22:15,170
他是我朋友  是我朋友  求求你們
He's my friend. He's my friend... Please.

1306
01:22:30,710 --> 01:22:32,180
求你們了  讓我...
Please, let me just...

1307
01:22:40,170 --> 01:22:41,240
上帝啊
Jesus!

1308
01:22:41,240 --> 01:22:42,530
不
No.

1309
01:22:43,620 --> 01:22:45,280
這不是真的
God, no.

1310
01:23:45,540 --> 01:23:51,320
冒牌天才自殺

1311
