你曾經對我說過
You... you told me once...

1332
01:26:03,250 --> 01:26:04,770
你不是個英雄
that you weren't a hero.

1333
01:26:06,950 --> 01:26:08,360
我也曾一度以為你不是人
There were times I didn't even think you were human,

1334
01:26:08,360 --> 01:26:10,640
但我要對你說  你是...
but let me tell you this, you were...

1335
01:26:11,480 --> 01:26:12,640
我認識的...
the best man...

1336
01:26:13,570 --> 01:26:18,250
最出色...最有人情味的人
the most human... human being that I've ever known

1337
