But, please, there's just one more thing, one more thing,

1342
01:26:45,800 --> 01:26:49,960
就一個奇跡  夏洛克  為了我  求你不要...
one more miracle, Sherlock, for me, don't be...

1343
01:26:51,640 --> 01:26:52,810
不要死
dead.

1344
